{
  "text": "Well, I did have a question on what you meant by the \"third spiral\" and if that is too long I would just ask if there is anything that we can do to make the instrument more comfortable or improve the contact? I am Ra. We may answer briefly. You may query in more detail if you deem it desirable at another session. If you picture the candle flame, you may see the third spiral. This instrument is well balanced. The accoutrements are aligned well. You are conscientious. I am Ra. I leave you, my friends, in the love and in the light of the One Infinite Creator. Go forth, therefore, rejoicing in the power and the peace of the One Infinite Creator. Adonai.",
